1
00:00:16,168 --> 00:00:21,697
<i>I want to try and gather</i>
<i>the unrestrained winds</i>

2
00:00:21,774 --> 00:00:26,507
<i>I'll run toward the horizon,</i>
<i>alongside the wave crests</i>

3
00:00:26,579 --> 00:00:29,139
