<i>What were you gazing at?</i>

10
00:01:16,529 --> 00:01:21,023
<i>What were you gazing at?</i>

11
00:01:49,695 --> 00:01:50,525
Where's Naruto?

12
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:52,893
It's no good.
I can't find him.

13
00:01:53,699 --> 00:01:54,324
